                <p>Backbone controllers for smartphones come in black and white, but if you've been looking for something more vibrant, then you can pick two limited-edition colorways right now. Available exclusively through Target, you can choose from the $170 <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=New+Backbone+Colorways+Give+The+Smartphone+Controllers+A+Cozy+Makeover&amp;fnauthor=darranged&amp;fndate=2025-10-03+05%3A16%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-10-03+05%3A16%3A36&amp;fnarticle_id=6535164&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=-&amp;fntype3=-&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgoto.target.com%2Fc%2F1804712%2F81938%2F2092%3FsubId1%3Dsubid_value%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fbackbone-pro-mauve-mobile-game-controller%2F-%2FA-94734456&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fnew-backbone-colorways-give-the-smartphone-controllers-a-cozy-makeover%2F1100-6535164%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Backbone Pro: Pink Edition </a>or a $100 <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=New+Backbone+Colorways+Give+The+Smartphone+Controllers+A+Cozy+Makeover&amp;fnauthor=darranged&amp;fndate=2025-10-03+05%3A16%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-10-03+05%3A16%3A36&amp;fnarticle_id=6535164&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=-&amp;fntype3=-&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgoto.target.com%2Fc%2F1804712%2F81938%2F2092%3FsubId1%3Dsubid_value%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fbackbone-one-usb-c-dream-purple-mobile-game-controller%2F-%2FA-94734454&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fnew-backbone-colorways-give-the-smartphone-controllers-a-cozy-makeover%2F1100-6535164%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Backbone One: Purple Edition controller</a>. These will go on sale soon, with online orders starting on October 5 and in-store sales starting on October 6.</p><div title="Backbone Cozy Colors Editions" data-embed-type="buylink" data-ref-id="4554" data-te