a modern-day controller are here, so you can jump right into a game of Genshin Impact or Call of Duty.</p><p>App functionality also expands on the functionality of the Backbone Pro, and overall, <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/backbone-pro-is-a-larger-more-customizable-version-of-the-best-mobile-controller/1100-6531316/">this model improves</a> on the ergonomics and customization of the original Backbone One.</p></div>                      </div>                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=New+Backbone+Colorways+Give+The+Smartphone+Controllers+A+Cozy+Makeover&amp;fnauthor=darranged&amp;fndate=2025-10-03+05%3A16%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-10-03+05%3A16%3A36&amp;fnarticle_id=6535164&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=-&amp;fntype3=-&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgoto.target.com%2Fc%2F1804712%2F81938%2F2092%3FsubId1%3Dsubid_value%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fbackbone-one-usb-c-dream-purple-mobile-game-controller%2F-%2FA-94734454&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fnew-backbone-colorways-give-the-smartphone-controllers-a-cozy-makeover%2F1100-6535164%2F&amp;event_type=click" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/clicks.trx-hub.com\/xid\/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=New+Backbone+Colorways+Give+The+Smartphone+Controllers+A+Cozy+Makeover&amp;fnauthor=darranged&amp;fndate=2025-10-03+05%3A16%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-10-03+05%3A16%3A36&amp;fnarticle_id=6535164&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=-&amp;fntype3=-&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgoto.target.com%2Fc%2F1804712%2F81938%2F2092%3FsubId1%3Dsubid_value%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fbackbone-one-usb-c-dream-purple-mobile-game-controller%2F-%2FA-94734454&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fnew-backbone-colorways-give-the-smartphone-controllers-a-cozy-makeover%2F1100-6535164%2F&amp;event_type=click&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=New+Backbone+Colorways+Give+The+Smartphone+Controllers+A+Cozy+Makeover&amp;fnauthor=darranged&amp;fndate=2025-10-03+05%3A16%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-10-03+05%3A16%3A36&amp;fnarticle_id=6535164&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=-&amp;fntype3=-&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgoto.target.com%2Fc%2F1804712%2F81938%2F2092%3FsubId1%3Dsubid_value%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fbackbone-one-usb-c-dream-purple-mobile-game-controller%2F-%2FA-94734454&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fnew-backbone-colorways-give-the-smartphone-controllers-a-cozy-makeover%2F1100-6535164%2F&amp;event_type=click">Backbone One: Purple Edition</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=New+Backbone+Colorways+Give+The+Smartphone+Controllers+A+Cozy+Makeover&amp;fnauthor=darranged&amp;fndate=2025-10-03+05%3A16%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-10-03+05%3A16%3A36&amp;fnarticle_id=6535164&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=-&amp;fntype3=-&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgoto.target.com%2Fc%2F1804712%2F81938%2F2092%3FsubId1%3Dsubid_value%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fbackbone-one-usb-c-dream-purple-mobile-game-controller%2F-%2FA-94734454&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fnew-backbone-colorways-give-the-smartphone-controllers-a-cozy-makeover%2F1100-6535164%2F&amp;event_type=click" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/clicks.trx-hub.com\/xid\/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=New+Backbone+Colorways+Give+The+Smartphone+Controllers+A+Cozy+Makeover&amp;fnauthor=darranged&amp;fndate=2025-10-03+05%3A16%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-10-03+05%3A16%3A36&amp;fnarticle_id=6535164&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=-&amp;fntype3=-&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgoto.target.com%2Fc%2F1804712%2F81938%2F2092%3FsubId1%3Dsubid_value%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fbackbone-one-usb-c-dream-purple-mobile-game-controller%2F-%2FA-94734454&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fnew-backbone-colorways-give-the-smartphone-controllers-a-cozy-makeover%2F1100-6535164%2F&amp;event_type=click&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=New+Backbone+Colorways+Give+The+Smartphone+Controllers+A+Cozy+Makeover&amp;fnauthor=darranged&amp;fndate=2025-10-03+05%3A16%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-10-03+05%3A16%3A36&amp;fnarticle_id=6535164&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=-&amp;fntype3=-&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgoto.target.com%2Fc%2F1804712%2F81938%2F2092%3FsubId1%3Dsubid_value%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fbackbone-one-usb-c-dream-purple-mobile-game-controller%2F-%2FA-94734454&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fnew-backbone-colorways-give-the-smartphone-controllers-a-cozy-makeover%2F1100-6535164%2F&amp;event_type=click">$100</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <p>While the Backbone One isn't as advanced, it's still a budget-friendly controller that can easily give you a traditional gaming experience on your smartphone. The design has been tweaked to feel more comfortable in your hands, and these Gen 2 controllers use an enhanced D-pad and face buttons that Backbone claims are more responsive. Using one is very easy, as all you have to do is snap it onto your smartphone and you're good to go. You don't even need to remove the protective cover of your smartphone, and these devices are compatible with PlayStation Remote Play, Xbox Cloud Gaming, and other streaming services. </p>                      </div>   </div><p>If the colors above don't appeal to you, then you can pick up a Backbone Pro or a <a href="https://www.amazon.com/BACKBONE-Mobile-Gaming-Controller-Android-iOS/dp/B0CCT2LWT8?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="nofollow ">Backbone One</a> in neutral shades of black and white. These are priced the same as the models above, as you can get a Gen 2 Backbone One for $100 or a <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Backbone-Gaming-Controller-Bluetooth-Pro-Level-Console/dp/B0DQM23MLZ?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="nofollow ">Backbone Pro for $170</a>.</p><h2>Backbone One</h2><p><strong>Gen 2 (USB-C)</strong></p><ul><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/BACKBONE-Mobile-Gaming-Controller-Android-iOS/dp/B0CCT2LWT8?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="nofollow ">Black</a> -- $100</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/BACKBONE-Mobile-Gaming-Controller-Android-iOS/dp/B0CCT2TJW4?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="nofollow ">White</a> -- $100</li></ul><p><strong>Gen 2 (Lightning)</strong></p><ul><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/BACKBONE-Mobile-Gaming-Controller-Android-iOS/dp/B0CT1BRLZ9?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="nofollow ">Black</a> -- $100</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/BACKBONE-Mobile-Gaming-Controller-Android-iOS/dp/B0CT17GPNT?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="nofollow ">White</a> -- $100</li></ul><h2>Backbone Pro</h2><ul><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Backbone-Gaming-Controller-Bluetooth-Pro-Level-Console/dp/B0DQM23MLZ?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="nofollow ">Black</a> -- $170</li></ul><p>Anyone using a tablet device can also check out the Razer <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Kishi-Gaming-Controller-Android-Tablets-Smartphone/dp/B0DVKWZ5SX?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Kishi V3 Pro XL</a>. This line of controllers from Razer recently launched, and while they are pricier, they do feature high-end components.</p><p>The Kishi V3 Pro XL is designed specifically for larger tablets--including 11- and 13-inch iPad Pro and Air models--while the Razer Kishi V3 Pro features the same hardware and is geared toward smaller 8-inch tablets and iPhones.</p><div data-embed-type="pinbox" data-ref-id="4304">  <ul>                              <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/amazon-audible-premium-plus-sign-up-prime-big-deal-days-black-friday-holiday-2025-deal/1100-6524536/">Audible Premium Plus Holiday Deal: Get 3 Audiobooks For $3</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/amazon-prime-big-deal-days-4k-blu-ray-best-deals/1100-6535093/">Get Popular Movies On 4K Blu-Ray For $15 Or Less At Amazon This Week</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/rog-xbox-ally-preorder-guide/1100-6535007/">ROG Xbox Ally X Preorders In Stock At Best Buy, Sold Out Everywhere Else (September 27)</a></li>                          <li>         <span>+ Show More More Gaming, Tech, and Entertainment Deals &amp; Preorders Links (5)</span>       </li>          <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/final-fantasy-magic-the-gathering-trading-cards-restock-where-to-buy-amazon-walmart-best-buy-target/2900-6271/">New Magic: The Gathering Final Fantasy Chocobo Bundle &amp; Scene Boxes Up For Preorder</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/lego-game-boy-restocked-at-amazon-and-its-shipping-early/1100-6533358/">You Can Get The $60 Lego Game Boy Early F